

In POSTMAN -
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
@PostMapping - addProduct

Set to Post - http://localhost:9090/productController/addProduct

{
	"productName": "Indi Tandoori Paneer Pizza ",
    "productDesc": "Include spicy Indian Paneer with mayo",
    "price": 370
}

{
    "productName": "Chicken Tandoori Pizza L",
    "productDesc": "Include Chicken Roasted on Pizza",
